snippet.title: A Brand New Cultural Settlement! Feudal Japan | Forge of Empires
snippet.description:
► Play Forge of Empires now: http://InnoGam.es/h92Q !

Available subtitles:EN, DE, FR, IT, ES (ES/MX), PL, PT (PT/BR), NL, CZ/SK, DK, FI, GR, HU, NO, RO, RU, SE, TH, TR 

Game Designers Micha and Kurt introduce the brand new Cultural Settlement to reach Forge of Empires: Feudal Japan!

Follow the ship that's on your shores to find an idyllic Feudal Japanese village waiting to progress!
